                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 20437/114.</note>
                <head>[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-08-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 16, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Department intends to send early in September one of its commercial advisers
                    to cooperate with you regarding the potash question, the settlement of which
                    apparently demands further diplomatic action.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
